race.comment: WINSOME STORM (2) missed the frame latest when fifth at Wentworth Park (30.49) but scored three back at this track (29.79). Strike rate this course and distance strong having won three of four tries. Can discover winning form. TUMBY BAY (4) could manage only fourth at Nowra last time but impressed when posting a speedy 22.82 over 401m at this track the start prior. Top win two back and can measure up again. MAXIMUS MERIDIUS (8) recorded a 1.5 lengths win (22.94) in a Grade 5 last time at this track. Suited here and expected to run well. CASH ME OUT (1) looks an each-way chance.
